<br>
1) Fed Ex type of quests: One of the officers gives the quester an item or set of items to deliver to other members of the guild in varying places around the world. Gets them meeting other members of the guild and gets them out and about<br>
2) Rescue quests: One of your officers (or willing members) is trapped in one of the dungeons and you must send a group into the dungeon to rescue them<br>
3) Storyline quests: Come up with a large story arc, and split that into multiple quests. Usually involves a few someone's in your guild creating evil alts and /dueling the questers, but can be a lot of fun <p>Haemish MacLennan<br>
